## Summary
The User Privacy API enables programmatic deletion of user data across Amplitude projects or organizations to comply with privacy laws like GDPR and CCPA, allowing deletion requests for up to 100 users at a time via Amplitude IDs or User IDs, with deletion jobs scheduled within 30 days of request.

